1347
01:32:34.429 --> 01:32:37.599
Yes, I would. I've arranged
for you to have an apartment,

1348
01:32:37.682 --> 01:32:40.643
have a car,
have a wide variety of stores

1349
01:32:40.769 --> 01:32:43.605
