1379
01:34:29.752 --> 01:34:31.838
Edward, his nuts
are on the block.

1380
01:34:31.921 --> 01:34:33.339
We got him.

1381
01:34:33.423 --> 01:34:35.300
<i>He's really caving in.</i>

1382
01:34:35.383 --> 01:34:38.136
<i>I want him to commit his stocks
to us this afternoon.</i>

1383
01:34:38.219 --> 01:34:41.306
