I don't want to wait.

1384
01:34:41.389 --> 01:34:44.100
Have Morse meet me downtown
this morning. Goodbye.

1385
01:34:52.233 --> 01:34:54.903
I have to go now.

1386
01:34:54.986 --> 01:34:56.905
I want you to understand.

1387
01:34:59.157 --> 01:35:01.034
