1394
01:35:30.271 --> 01:35:32.065
Barnard Thompson, Miss Vivian.

1395
01:35:32.148 --> 01:35:33.983
Could you come to
the front desk?

1396
01:35:34.067 --> 01:35:36.527
Someone here
wants to speak to you.

1397
01:35:36.653 --> 01:35:38.988
- Her name is Miss DE Luca.
