1408
01:36:22.031 --> 01:36:24.200
Yeah, they told me
at the Banana.

1409
01:36:24.325 --> 01:36:27.578
- You were supposed to come Tuesday.
- I was hiding from Carlos.

1410
01:36:27.662 --> 01:36:30.206
